"SECTION 10. Arkansas Code ยง 23-99-1129 is amended to read as follows:
23-99-1129. Appeals process for disallowance of prior authorization.
(a) If the Arkansas State Board of Pharmacy and the Arkansas State
Medical Board, jointly, disallow a prior authorization of a prescription
drug, medicine, biological product, pharmaceutical, or pharmaceutical service
requested under ยง 23-99-1128, a healthcare insurer, pharmacy benefits
